---
title: Chicken Lettuce Tomato Burger with DIY Ranch and Roasted Sweet Potatoes
description: We've upped the ante on this classic chicken burger with succulent chicken breast, lemon pepper spice,  and a fresh DIY chive ranch sauce — there's never a dull moment in this weeknight winner!
